_sText:
Hello everyone. This is my first published map. Its a map by houses, and a hidden underground network. It is like six enterable buildings, none made by me, so thank you very much who ever made this prefabs. I just made the prefabs fit my map and made some few changes on it. ;) I hope you will give it a try and give me feedback! I will start working on v3 very soon.

If you add the this map to your server, please give me the IP, i want to play on the map with others then my mates and bots. ; O 

If you got any Q's about the map, I got the A's. :)

out

-Zhakti
